#!/bin/sh ip addr add 201.0.0.2/24 dev eth0 ip addr add 10.10.1.161/28 dev eth1 ip route add 10.10.0.0/24 via 10.10.1.162 dev eth1 ip route add 10.10.1.128/27 via 10.10.1.162 dev eth1 ip route add 10.10.1.0/25 via 10.10.1.162 dev eth1 ip route add default via 201.0.0.1 dev eth0
iptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING -s 10.10.1.0/25 -o eth0 -j MASQUERADE iptables -t filter -A FORWARD -o eth0 -s 10.10.1.0/25 -j ACCEPT iptables -t filter -A FORWARD -s 10.10.1.163 -d 201.0.2.2 -j REJECT iptables -t filter -A FORWARD -j DROP -o eth0

#!/bin/sh ip addr add 201.0.1.2/24 dev eth0 ip addr add 10.10.0.1/24 dev eth1 ip route add 10.10.1.160/28 via 10.10.0.2 dev eth1 ip route add 10.10.1.128/27 via 10.10.0.2 dev eth1 ip route add 10.10.1.0/25 via 10.10.0.2 dev eth1 ip route add default via 201.0.1.1 dev eth0
iptables -t filter -A FORWARD -s 10.10.0.0/24 -o eth0 -j ACCEPT iptables -t filter -A FORWARD -d 201.0.2.2/24 -o eth0 -j ACCEPT
#iptables -t filter -A FORWARD -d 10.10.0.0/24 -o eth0 -j ACCEPT
iptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING -o eth0 -j MASQUERADE
iptables -t filter -A FORWARD -s 10.10.1.163 -j REJECT
iptables -t nat -A PREROUTING -i eth0 -p tcp --dport 80 -j DNAT --to-destination 10.10.0.3:80 iptables -A FORWARD -d 10.10.0.3 -p tcp --dport 80 -j ACCEPT

#!/bin/sh ip addr add 192.168.10.1/24 dev eth0 ip addr add 201.0.2.2/24 dev eth1 ip route add default via 201.0.2.1 dev eth1
iptables -t filter -A FORWARD -s 192.168.10.0/24 -o eth0 -j ACCEPT iptables -t filter -A FORWARD -d 192.168.10.0/24 -i eth0 -j ACCEPT iptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING -o eth1 -j MASQUERADE

#!/bin/sh ip addr add 10.10.1.162/28 dev eth0 ip addr add 10.10.0.2/24 dev eth1 ip addr add 10.10.1.129/27 dev eth2 ip route add 10.10.1.0/25 via 10.10.1.130 dev eth2 ip route add 201.0.2.2 via 10.10.0.1 dev eth1 ip route add default via 10.10.1.161 dev eth0
